===== Description =====

This repository contains a serie of reusable modules regarding weightless neural networks and some other utilities.

===== Dependencies =====

doxygen

===== Installing =====

This is a template library and in order to use it you must add the library path to your CPLUS_INCLUDE_PATH.
This can be accomplished by inserting the following line to your ~/.bashrc 

export CPLUS_INCLUDE_PATH="$CPLUS_INCLUDE_PATH:$HOME/PATH_TO_THIS_LIB>/include"

===== Documentation =====

type "make doc" to generate the documentation

